rComments: Her tests and exams are super fair. Everything you need to know is in the slides that she posts. You will have to read the slides and go to class in order to do well in the course but if you miss one class is no biggie because she is pretty detailed in her slides.

Her tests were easy given that you put in the effort to study. It's important to take good notes in class as that really helps when it comes time to study but the exam was quite tricky even though the content was easy and understandable.
